College_Summary: Kennesaw State University is a public, research university located in metropolitan Atlanta in Georgia. With 2 campuses in Kennesaw and Marietta, the school is the third largest university in the state of Georgia. It is home to approximately 43,000 students. College_Heading: University of New Orleans: Rankings, Courses, Admissions, Tuition Fee, Cost of Attendance & Scholarships
